      <title>摩根大通交易部门表示“接近”逢低买入机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/jpm-trading-desk-says-getting-close-to-buy-the-dip-opportunity-lzh07hst</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着周一全球股市抛售加剧，摩根大通交易部门表示，科技股的轮换可能“基本完成”，市场“正在接近”逢低买入的战术机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/jpm-trading-desk-says-getting-close-to-buy-the-dip-opportunity-lzh07hst</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 13:05:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>嘉能可腐败调查以瑞士罚款结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/glencore-ordered-to-pay-150-million-by-swiss-in-criminal-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士当局结束对这家大宗商品交易商和矿业公司的调查后，嘉能可公司将支付 1.52 亿美元，这标志着欧洲和美洲长达六年多的法律调查结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/glencore-ordered-to-pay-150-million-by-swiss-in-criminal-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 12:26:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大陆集团考虑剥离汽车零部件业务，进行重大重组</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/continental-weighs-spinning-off-struggling-automotive-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大陆集团正考虑剥离并上市陷入困境的汽车零部件业务，以将其与更为成功的轮胎业务区分开来，这将成为这家德国公司 152 年历史上最大的重组。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/continental-weighs-spinning-off-struggling-automotive-unit</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 11:40:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
